*Dođemo* li u pet, bilo bi super. (If we come at five, it would be great.)

Sutra ćemo *doći* u školu. (We will come to school tomorrow.)

Uveče ću *doći* po tebe. (I will come for you in the evening.)

*Dođoh* da te pitam nešto. (I came to ask you something.)

Idemo u park, *dođi* sa nama! (Let's go to the park, come with us!)